{"tid":2066873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好叫自己做「自由閪」","createTime":"2020-06-16T14:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T15:02:48.000Z","uid":360675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f6910e0a39e287b72e510750f77ea6bbd734f2","tid":2066873,"uid":360675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"喺fb見到有個page，啲畫幾靚嘅，啲主題都係香港抗爭，但其中有張圖，入面設計有用到「自由閪」，就覺得好哽眼，因為呢個詞語係敵人用嚟嘲笑、貶低我哋，我哋無理由用嚟形容翻自己，就正如我哋唔會叫自己做「曱甴」、黑警死都唔認自己係有牌爛仔（雖然佢哋係），啲黑警咁鍾意掛嘢喺個身，都唔會見到佢哋會掛住「販冰兵」、「極醜惡」、「二等公安」、「警曱」喺個身上。（雖然佢哋的確係）<br />\n<br />\n見過有人整貼紙、整衫都用呢個詞，希望注意下，唔好再用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下畫圖取至 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101884464535694/posts/299123511478454/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101884464535694%2Fposts%2F299123511478454%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=6b8f45ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101884464535694/posts/299123511478454/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnOCFVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnOCFVQ.jpg&h=52aa981c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9d73970bb6c7e6e35d4201153d31523656796af","tid":2066873,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"是旦啦，咪由得班傻閪咁嗌自己囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b7093cddc8ad3d6cff5e131f0081080c4e26d2","tid":2066873,"uid":109629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"上年見過有張文宣寫：「就算我地係曱甴，都係一隻有良知既曱甴」然後配個有曱甴觸鬚既黃色頭盔公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我心諗係咪short q左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整出黎俾對家笑咩"},{"pid":"6175099362cf0199b1cdcd2f6b95b969bcfb301b","tid":2066873,"uid":360675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4b7093cddc8ad3d6cff5e131f00810